VALUES (@p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, 0),
(@p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, 1),
(@p15, @p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, 2),

INSERT ([Color], [IsDeleted], [OrderId], [Price], [ProductName], [ShopId])

INTO @inserted0;

ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

INSERT ([Color], [IsDeleted], [OrderId], [Price], [ProductName], [ShopId])

INTO @inserted0;

ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

CREATE TABLE [Products] (
    [ProductId] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [ProductName] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [Color] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [IsDeleted] bit NOT NULL,
    [Price] int NOT NULL,
    [ShopId] int NOT NULL,
    [OrderId] int NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Products] PRIMARY KEY ([ProductId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([OrderId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Shops_ShopId] FOREIGN KEY ([ShopId]) REFERENCES [Shops] ([ShopId]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

MERGE [Products] USING (
VALUES (@p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, 1),
(@p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, 2),
(@p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, 3),
(@p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, 4)) AS i ([Color], [IsDeleted], [Price], [ProductName], [ShopId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Color], [IsDeleted], [Price], [ProductName], [ShopId])

OUTPUT INSERTED.[ProductId], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([ProductId] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Products] USING (
VALUES (@p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, 1),
(@p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, 2),
(@p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, 3),
(@p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, 4)) AS i ([Color], [IsDeleted], [Price], [ProductName], [ShopId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Color], [IsDeleted], [Price], [ProductName], [ShopId])
VALUES (i.[Color], i.[IsDeleted], i.[Price], i.[ProductName], i.[ShopId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[ProductId], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

VALUES (@p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, 1),
(@p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, 2),

SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Price], [o].[小ompleted], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Color], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductName], [t].[ShopId]

) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrdersOrderId], [o].[ProductsProductId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Price], [o0].[小ompleted]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [Orders] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrdersOrderId] = [o0].[OrderId]
) AS [t] ON [p].[ProductId] = [t].[ProductsProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[ProductId], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId]

CREATE TABLE [AspNetUsers] (
    [Id] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [RealName] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [LastName] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [ImageName] nvarchar(100) NULL,
    [UserName] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [NormalizedUserName] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [Email] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [NormalizedEmail] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [EmailConfirmed] bit NOT NULL,
    [PasswordHash] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [SecurityStamp] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [ConcurrencyStamp] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [PhoneNumber] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [PhoneNumberConfirmed] bit NOT NULL,
    [TwoFactorEnabled] bit NOT NULL,
    [LockoutEnd] datetimeoffset NULL,
    [LockoutEnabled] bit NOT NULL,
    [AccessFailedCount] int NOT NULL,

) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]

) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId]

) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId]

SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Price], [o].[小ompleted], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Color], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductName], [t].[ShopId]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId]

) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]

    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId]

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([OrderId] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Orders] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, 0),
(@p2, @p3, 1),
(@p4, @p5, 2),
(@p6, @p7, 3),
(@p8, @p9, 4)) AS i ([Price], [小ompleted], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Price], [小ompleted])
VALUES (i.[Price], i.[小ompleted])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[OrderId], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

    [ShopName] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,

);

CREATE TABLE [Products] (
    [ProductId] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [ProductName] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [Color] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [IsDeleted] bit NOT NULL,
    [Price] int NOT NULL,
    [ShopId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Products] PRIMARY KEY ([ProductId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Shops_ShopId] FOREIGN KEY ([ShopId]) REFERENCES [Shops] ([ShopId]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
CREATE TABLE [OrderProduct] (
    [OrdersOrderId] int NOT NULL,
    [ProductsProductId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_OrderProduct] PRIMARY KEY ([OrdersOrderId], [ProductsProductId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_OrderProduct_Orders_OrdersOrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrdersOrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([OrderId]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_OrderProduct_Products_ProductsProductId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductsProductId]) REFERENCES [Products] ([ProductId]) ON DELETE CASCADE

Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Price], [o].[小ompleted], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Color], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductName], [t].[ShopId]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]

    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]

CREATE TABLE [Shops] (
    [ShopId] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [ShopName] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [StoreAddress] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [UserId] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Shops] PRIMARY KEY ([ShopId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Shops_AspNetUsers_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [AspNetUsers] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
CREATE TABLE [Products] (
    [ProductId] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [ProductName] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [Color] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [IsDeleted] bit NOT NULL,
    [Price] int NOT NULL,
    [ShopId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Products] PRIMARY KEY ([ProductId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Shops_ShopId] FOREIGN KEY ([ShopId]) REFERENCES [Shops] ([ShopId]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
CREATE TABLE [OrderProduct] (
    [OrdersOrderId] int NOT NULL,
    [ProductsProductId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_OrderProduct] PRIMARY KEY ([OrdersOrderId], [ProductsProductId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_OrderProduct_Orders_OrdersOrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrdersOrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([OrderId]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_OrderProduct_Products_ProductsProductId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductsProductId]) REFERENCES [Products] ([ProductId]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]

SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Price], [o].[小ompleted], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Color], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductName], [t].[ShopId]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId]

(DbType = Boolean), @p6='?' (DbType = Int32), @p7='?' (DbType = Boolean), @p8='?' (DbType = Int32), @p9='?' (DbType = Boolean), @p10='?' (Size = 50), @p11='?' (Size = 50), @p12='?' SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([OrderId] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Orders] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, 0),
(@p2, @p3, 1),
(@p4, @p5, 2),
(@p6, @p7, 3),
(@p8, @p9, 4)) AS i ([Price], [小ompleted], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Price], [小ompleted])
VALUES (i.[Price], i.[小ompleted])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[OrderId], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [i].[OrderId] FROM @inserted0 i
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted5 TABLE ([ShopId] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Shops] USING (
VALUES (@p10, @p11, @p12, 0),
(@p13, @p14, @p15, 1)) AS i ([ShopName], [StoreAddress], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([ShopName], [StoreAddress], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[ShopName], i.[StoreAddress], i.[UserId])

Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Price], [o].[小ompleted], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Color], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductName], [t].[ShopId]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[OrdersOrderId], [o0].[ProductsProductId], [p].[ProductId], [p].[Color], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ShopId]
    FROM [OrderProduct] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductsProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrdersOrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrdersOrderId], [t].[ProductsProductId]
